Question: Should restaurant be required to display nutritional information in their menu?
Answer:
from my stand point of view, i prefer the restaurants to display nutritional information in their menu. below are the evidences to support my opinion. first of all, there are so many people with different health problems, it is essential for them to know about what they take in the restaurants. in addition, it is the customers right to know about the details of what they purchase from the restaurants.